Description[en]=The server from which the home directory of the user is mounted is configured with the variable 'samba/homedirserver'. This variable configures the directory on that server where the home directory of the user resides. With '%U' the current username is expanded and used. If 'samba/homedirserver' and 'samba/homedirserver' are set to 'local', no home directory is mounted.
Type=str
Categories=service-samba

